Package: calaminer
Title: Fast Excel File Reader Using Rust
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Maximilian", "Manek", email = "maximilian.manek@hotmail.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: High-performance Excel file reader supporting xlsx, xlsm, xlsb,
    xls, and ods formats. Built on the Rust 'calamine' library, providing
    significantly faster read times compared to pure R implementations.
    Supports reading sheet names, dimensions, and data as data frames.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mmanek/calaminer
BugReports: https://github.com/mmanek/calaminer/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc >= 1.75.0
Config/rextendr/version: 0.3.1
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
